OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FIran's Supreme Leader, Ayatollah Ali
OL,7,FKhamenei, long a target of the US and
OL,8,FIsrael, was killed during coordinated
OL,9,Fdaytime strikes on Tehran on Saturday
OL,10,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
