OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FFollowing the attack on targets across
OL,7,FIran, including one on the offices of
OL,8,FKhamenei, US President Donald Trump
OL,9,Fannounced on social media that "one of
OL,10,Fthe most evil people in History, is
OL,11,Fdead". After initially dismissing
OL,12,FTrump's statement as "false rumours",
OL,13,FIranian state TV admitted on Sunday
OL,14,Fmorning that the Supreme Leader, the
OL,15,FIslamic Republic's second in its 47-
OL,16,Fyear history, had been killed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
