PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772444181
OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FIranians across the country are still
OL,7,Freeling from shock, grief and fear
OL,8,Fafter the nationwide protests were
OL,9,Fcrushed by the deadliest crackdown
OL,10,Fever seen under the rule of the 86-
OL,11,Fyear-old Khamenei. Thousands were
OL,12,Fkilled and tens of thousands are
OL,13,Fbelieved to have been arrested.
OL,15,FKhamenei appeared on state television
OL,16,Facknowledging that thousands had been
OL,17,Fkilled but blamed foreign influence -
OL,18,Fespecially his longtime enemies,
OL,19,FIsrael and the US. His response drew
OL,20,Fire from within Iran and around the
OL,21,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772444181
OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FJanuary's protests were just the
OL,7,Flatest in ever-larger waves of mass
OL,8,Fprotests under Khamenei's rule. Anger
OL,9,Fover the 2022 death of Mahsa Amini,
OL,10,Fdetained for not wearing her mandatory
OL,11,Fheadscarf properly, escalated into
OL,12,Fdemonstrations against social
OL,13,Frestrictions. During January's
OL,14,Fprotests, marchers across the country
OL,15,Fchanted, "Death to Khamenei."
OL,17,FBut he was revered by many, too, for
OL,18,Fhis remoulding of the Islamic
OL,19,FRepublic, which he took charge of
OL,20,Ffollowing the death of Ayatollah
OL,21,FRuhollah Khomeini in 1989.
OL,26,@wD@JOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
