OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FHe greatly expanded the Shiite
OL,7,Fclerical class and built the
OL,8,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard into
OL,9,Fa ruthless force that underpinned his
OL,10,Frule. The Guard became a military and
OL,11,Fbusiness behemoth, with a powerful
OL,12,Fgrip on Iran's economy.
OL,14,FWho was Ali Khamenei?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
