OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FThe Islamic scholar had been Iran's
OL,7,FSupreme Leader since 1989, succeeding
OL,8,Fthe Islamic Republic's late founder,
OL,9,FAyatollah Ruhollah Khomeini. As
OL,10,FSupreme Leader, Khamenei held ultimate
OL,11,Fauthority over all branches of
OL,12,Fgovernment, the military and the
OL,13,Fjudiciary.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
