PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772444181
OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FBorn to an impoverished family of
OL,7,Fclerics, far away from the Iranian
OL,8,Fcapital, Tehran, Khamenei, like many
OL,9,Fother Iranian leaders, studied under
OL,10,FKhomeini at the seminary in the holy
OL,11,Fcity of Qom, south of Tehran, in the
OL,12,Fearly 1960s, before Khomeini's exile
OL,13,Fto Iraq and France.
OL,15,FThe young Khamenei was radicalised in
OL,16,Fthe dying years of the Shah, and was
OL,17,Fby Khomeini's side when he returned to
OL,18,FIran to lead the 1979 revolution.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
