OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772444181
OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FA year after the revolution and the
OL,7,Ffounding of the Islamic Republic, Iran
OL,8,Fwas at war with its neighbour,fs Iraq,
OL,9,Fa conflict that would drag on for
OL,10,Feight years, leaving more than a
OL,11,Fmillion dead.
OL,13,FIn 1981, a year into the war, Khamenei
OL,14,Fwas elected Iran's third president;
OL,15,Fthat same year, a bombing by opponents
OL,16,Fleft him with one hand paralysed.
OL,18,FJust a year after the war ended,
OL,19,FKhomeini died and Ali Khamenei was
OL,20,Fnamed his successor as Iran's Supreme
OL,21,FLeader.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
