PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772444181
OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FHe took power in 1989, making him one
OL,7,Fof the longest-serving leaders in the
OL,8,FMiddle East.
OL,10,FBut his greatest achievement was
OL,11,Ftransforming Iran from a regional
OL,12,Fpariah into a regional, even global,
OL,13,Fpower.
OL,15,FHe embedded Iranian influence by
OL,16,Festablishing powerful proxies, such as
OL,17,Fthe late Hamas leader Ismail Haniyeh -
OL,18,Fand through Hezbollah's late leader,
OL,19,FHassan Nasrallah.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772444181
OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FHe also developed Iran's nuclear
OL,7,Fprogramme, saying it was for civilian
OL,8,Fpurposes.
OL,10,FBut then the network of influence he'd
OL,11,Fbuilt began to crumble. After the
OL,12,FOctober 7, 2023 atrocity in Israel,
OL,13,FBenjamin Netanyahu took revenge for
OL,14,FAli Khamenei's support of Hamas and
OL,15,FHezbollah in Gaza and Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
