PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1772444181
OL,3,CWho was Iran's Supreme Leader Ali
OL,4,CKhamenei?
OL,6,FIran's economy was also in meltdown.
OL,7,FInternational sanctions lifted under
OL,8,Fthe 2015 nuclear deal began to be
OL,9,Freinstated and became a growing source
OL,10,Fof discontent among Iranians, as well
OL,11,Fas increasing impatience around the
OL,12,Fworld.
OL,14,FThe Ayatollah had survived last
OL,15,Fsummer's 12-day war with Israel after
OL,16,Fgoing into hiding but the target on
OL,17,Fhis back only grew larger.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
